metadata.name: Sockz (Edition 1) #1
metadata.description:
Sockz (Edition 1) are a free special-edition collectible exclusive to CrypToadz #4566 PartyBid contributors. The original PartyBid can be found at https://www.partybid.app/party/0xE43f0Bf1Fc7B5f8FA3c29b4B62294CA996C93D93. Ghost Sockz NFTs can be burned/redeemed for a spooky physical pair of Ghost Sockz sent to any door, any time. 

A SockzDAO & Ghost DAO Co-Production.
